review: Dr. Ranjith listens to your problem and understands the issue very well. He makes you very comfortable to deal with. My personal experience was very good , the way he explains the problem and makes us feel it's not a big deal to over come the problem is a very good attitude .he explains abt the treatment, action and follow up and he's always there for any emergencies. *** *** ******* **** ** ******* **** *********. thanks you so much doctor
reply_text: Thank you very much for your kind words.

review: Overall satisfied with the explanation given by doctor. He explained the problem in detail and suggested some exercises

Very nice and professional behavior, Relaxed environment and made us comfortable which is very important with respect to managing the patients.

Thanks for your inputs and suggestions Doctor.

I would strongly recommend the Doctor for anybody with Ortho related issues.
